-- Ceres Power Surges After Improvements to Fuel Cell Technology
-- B y   S a l l y   B a k e w e l l
-- 2012-01-23T10:52:24Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-23/ceres-power-surges-after-improvements-to-fuel-cell-technology.html
Ceres Power Holdings Plc (CWR)  rose the
most in two months after it announced improvements to its
technology for developing fuel cells.  The Horsham-based company rose as much as 41 percent today
to 11 pence ($0.17), the most since Nov. 16, following a
statement today. The stock traded at 10.5 pence at 10:49 a.m.
